summary: Basically, it increases the density of grass.
descriptionHtml:
Increases the density of grass.  

I recommend you use [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3288]Lush Grass[/url] by OpticShooter for, well, lusher grass! (His [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3385]Lush Trees[/url] mod is good, too)

I am aware of MannyGT\'s [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21525http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3385]Grass and Grass[/url] mod, but I am going to go for a different aspect of grass density, and maybe throw in new types of grass later on.

I really have no clue what it is compatible with, and what it isn\'t.  Should work with most, but not the ones that edit the density of grass.  If you want to point out what it isn\'t compatible with, say in the comments.

Link to this page for people using the NMM browser:  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/31505
author: Zealyfree
